{"tid":113233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【輕手唔犯法？】普京簽署新法例 家暴唔打到重傷唔算刑事","createTime":"2017-02-08T18:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T14:09:00.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7902426a11494cf7604f7acd716b3c07826df8d9","tid":113233,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T18:37:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>【輕手唔犯法？】普京簽署新法例 家暴唔打到重傷唔算刑事</strong><br />\n<br />\n2017-02-08 20:33:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京周二簽署新法例，放寬對家庭暴力的處罰，受害人若沒有受重傷，初犯者僅屬民事罪，而非刑事罪行。<br />\n<br />\n普京所屬的統一俄羅斯黨贊成新例，指可以保障家長教育兒童，並減少國家介入家庭事務，又指若受害人受重傷，犯案者仍需負刑事責任。克里姆林宮聲明指，法案在國會通過後，普京已正式簽署成為法例。<br />\n<br />\n婦女團體就擔心新修變相鼓勵家暴，又指法例倒退。根據聯合國2010年報告，每年有1.4萬名俄羅斯婦女死在丈夫或其親友手上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93aadd08fb3851bf3c5c50934e5dfcb31d75fb6","tid":113233,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T18:39:17.000Z","msg":"香港無重傷好多時判守行為就算"},{"pid":"8788bc55deb0c81b7ce1f3211883a51e38d65dce","tid":113233,"uid":35451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T18:47:57.000Z","msg":"每年有1.4萬名俄羅斯婦女死在丈夫或其親友手上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3699dd6f6b470963bfb7a98bc2fbb3444207ba68","tid":113233,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T18:51:52.000Z","msg":"嘩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  留名等睇美國女權份子出黎遣責普京<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢地緊係諗點整大女廁都唔得閒理極權國家D女人啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81f2fca791f9631705c5e97f0a3765f1144faff","tid":113233,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:25:19.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族是怎樣鍊成的"},{"pid":"96f01cb67add00028e920562905918d6ac23e886","tid":113233,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:48:31.000Z","msg":"老納<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c63f960d419f2b7292526aa08e3c26984fc6a2","tid":113233,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T20:17:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86a59bc55260ea9757b9b5e013805ddd5e08d145","tid":113233,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T21:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  留名等睇美國女權份子出黎遣責普京<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢地緊係諗點整大女廁都唔得閒理極權國家D女人啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實加拿大同美國家庭暴力<br />\n好多受害者都係男性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個時啲女權撚都唔知去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5acf56ade7a9ad1747c8b75518bec80b6634ef86","tid":113233,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T22:33:57.000Z","msg":"怪唔得知亞洲男係東歐咁受個到女人歡迎<br />\n個到d男人打老婆好勁"},{"pid":"19361628af7c25da0b34cbc1b39624a6bdc801a6","tid":113233,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:24:36.000Z","msg":"反普京同trump嘅都係左膠！"},{"pid":"77fb31a54d1c1c5f18b7a92ebd8125d42df2dbe6","tid":113233,"uid":54216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:27:36.000Z","msg":"俄佬要打到重傷有幾難，依條例係要佢地學下控制力度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas